Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.11,Serifu,,0000,0000,0000,,ไม่จริงน่า!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:53.76,Serifu,,0000,0000,0000,,จริงเหรอ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.11,Serifu,,0000,0000,0000,,จริงสิ!
